<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='306000' id='t-306000'>But by comparison,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='308000' id='t-308000'>we can learn.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='310000' id='t-310000'>We can learn by watching other people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='313000' id='t-313000'>and copying or imitating</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='315000' id='t-315000'>what they can do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='317000' id='t-317000'>We can then choose, from among a range of options,</span>
