<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='350000' id='t-350000'>even 1,000 or 2,000 years ago.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='353000' id='t-353000'>And all of this because of cumulative cultural adaptation.</span>
