<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420000' id='t-420000'>And the reason that dilemma arose</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422000' id='t-422000'>is, it turns out, that social learning is visual theft.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425000' id='t-425000'>If I can learn by watching you,</span>
