<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581000' id='t-581000'>for humans to exploit.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583000' id='t-583000'>And we take this utterly for granted,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='585000' id='t-585000'>because we're a species that is so at home with language,</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='588000' id='t-588000'>but you have to realize</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590000' id='t-590000'>that even the simplest acts of exchange that we engage in</span>
