<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='616000' id='t-616000'>So what you do is --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618000' id='t-618000'>one of those people has not really acquired language yet.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621000' id='t-621000'>And let's pretend the other one is good at language skills.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:34
