<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704000' id='t-704000'>If you look at our ancestors,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706000' id='t-706000'>the Neanderthals and the Homo erectus, our immediate ancestors,</span>
